@startuml state-simulation-job

skinparam defaultFontName Liberation Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

skinparam state {
  BorderColor #003087
  BackgroundColor #EEF3FA
  FontColor #003087
  ArrowColor #333333
  ArrowFontColor #555555
  ArrowFontSize 10
}

[*] --> Pending : POST /v1/jobs/quasi-extinction\n/ persist job record in DB

Pending : entry / assign job_id\ndo / wait for background worker

Pending --> Running : [background worker available]\n/ start Monte Carlo computation

Running : do / execute Monte Carlo simulation\n(100+ stochastic trajectories)

state choice <<choice>>
Running --> choice : computation ends

choice --> Completed : [no error]
choice --> Failed    : [unhandled exception]

Completed : entry / store probability curve results\ndo / make results available via GET /v1/jobs/{id}

Failed : entry / store error_message\ndo / expose error via GET /v1/jobs/{id}

Completed --> [*] : user deletes job\n/ DELETE /v1/jobs/{id}
Failed    --> [*] : user deletes job\n/ DELETE /v1/jobs/{id}

@enduml
